{"_id":"G1AcadKnowItAll0","name":"Know-It-All","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 0","description":"When this character fails a Skill Challenge with a Skill associated with a Mental Aspect, she may discard a card to immediately reflip that Challenge. If the discarded card was a Tome (t), she may use an Academic Skill of her choice in place of the original Skill."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1AcadStuOfKnow0","name":"Student of Knowledge","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 1","description":"Gains the following Trigger on all Academic Skill Duels: (t) Insight: After resolving, draw a card."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1AcadSciClass00","name":"Scientific Classification","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 1","description":"Gains the following Tactical Action: (1) Document Denizen: Target an enemy within 10 yards. Make a Challenge flip using Engineering (Construct), History (human), or Wilderness (everything else). Wilderness is Academic for this duel. Opposed by target's Deceive + Cunning + Rank Value. Success: learn target's type, Rank Value, and nature of Abilities/Talents. Rare/unique targets may impose a negative flip at Fatemaster's discretion. Cannot identify characters by name."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1AcadRationMnd0","name":"Rational Mind","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 3","description":"Choose an Academic Skill. When making a Challenge Flip to resist manipulation (terror, mind control, intimidation), add ranks in the chosen Skill to the final duel total."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1AcadSymposium0","name":"Symposium","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 3","description":"During an Ongoing Challenge, this character's Academic Skill final duel totals increase by +1 each time another character in the Ongoing Challenge succeeds at an Academic Skill Challenge. Bonus lasts until end of the Ongoing Challenge."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1AcadAnnoyDist0","name":"Annoying Distraction","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 5","description":"When this character successfully uses the Trick or Impose Action against an opponent during Dramatic Time, that opponent becomes Dazed until the start of this character's next turn."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1AcadBoringLect","name":"Boring Lecture","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 5","description":"With at least 5 minutes to lecture on a subject corresponding to an Academic Skill (rank >= 1), make a Challenge Flip using that Skill, opposed by Willpower duels of every non-Beast character that can hear her. If this character's total >= opponent's Willpower total: Dazed for 1 hour of Narrative Time. Margin of Success against any character: that character must attempt a TN 10 Unconsciousness Challenge."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1AcadLessLearn0","name":"Lessons Learned","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 7","description":"Gains the following Defensive Trigger: Df (t) Lessons Learned: After resolving against an enemy's attack, draw a card."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1AcadMentalCond","name":"Mental Conditioning","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 7","description":"Choose a Mental-based Skill and a Suit. Add the chosen Suit to that Skill's rank value."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1AcadPhilosoph0","name":"Philosopher","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 9","description":"Once per turn during Dramatic Time, after taking a Pass Action, this character may discard a card to draw a card."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1AcadErudition0","name":"Erudition","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 9","description":"This character may add her Intellect Aspect to the final duel total of every non-Magical Skill associated with a Mental Aspect."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1AcadEurekaMom0","name":"Eureka Moment","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Academic","requirements":"Step 10","description":"Once per session, this character may discard a card to deduce an important piece of information about a topic of her choice. Content is determined by the Fatemaster and should be practically useful."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
