{"_id":"G1CrimImprovise0","name":"Improvise","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 0","description":"This character may discard a card to create a shiv. The shiv lasts indefinitely until used; it breaks at the end of Dramatic Time after use. (Shiv: melee weapon — refer to rulebook for full stat block.)"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1CrimScoundrel0","name":"Scoundrel","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 1","description":"Gains the following Trigger on all Social Skill Challenges: (Mask) Fast Talk: After resolving, take a Pick Pocket Action against a target within 1 yard. The Pick Pocket Action gains a positive flip."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1CrimFrndLowPl0","name":"Friends in Low Places","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 1","description":"Gains a positive flip to Barter, Bewitch, and Leadership Challenges against bandits, gang members, criminals, mercenaries, and other lawless types. If a Fatemaster character pursues a bounty on this character, she learns about it from a contact as soon as possible."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1CrimRelentles0","name":"Relentless","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 3","description":"This character is immune to Horror Duels."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1CrimDuplicitou","name":"Duplicitous","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 3","description":"This character may use her Deceive Skill in place of Evade Skill when calculating her Defense Derived Aspect."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1CrimDirtyTrick","name":"Dirty Trick","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 5","description":"Gains the following Trigger on the Trick Action: (Mask) Dirty Trick: After succeeding, take a (1) AP Close Combat attack against the target, if in range."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1CrimThugs00000","name":"Thugs","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 5","description":"This character attracts 2 Thug subordinate characters. When using the (1) Order Action to command Thugs, may command both with different orders. When commanding a single Thug, the (1) Order Action becomes a (0) Action. Killed Thugs may be replaced at the start of the next session. Thug stats: Might 2, Grace 1, Speed 0, Resilience 2, Charm -3, Intellect 2, Cunning -1, Tenacity 2, Defense 4 (9), Willpower 4 (9), Walk 4, Charge 4, Initiative 1 (6), Wounds 6. Type: Minion (5), Living, Height 2. Skills: Evade 2, Intimidate 2, Melee 3, Notice 1, Toughness 1. Ability — Goons: When this character's controller succeeds on the (1) Trick Action, this Thug also gains the benefits. Ability — Pick On Someone Yer Own Size!: When this Thug's controller is targeted with a melee attack and this Thug would be a valid target, the controller may discard a card to make this Thug the target instead. Attack — (1) Crude Club (Melee): AV 5 (10), Range melee 2, Resist Df, Damage 2/2/4; Severe damage also inflicts a Weak Critical Effect."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1CrimStudyOpp00","name":"Study Opponent","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 7","description":"Choose Close Combat or Ranged Combat. When making an attack of the chosen type, this character may target the opponent's Willpower instead of Defense."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1CrimIntoShadow","name":"Into Shadow","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 7","description":"Choose Close Combat or Ranged Combat. Gains the following Trigger on all attacks of the chosen type: (Mask) Hide in Shadow: After succeeding, move up to 3 yards in any direction."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1CrimMisdirect0","name":"Misdirection","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 9","description":"Gains the following Defensive Trigger: Df (Mask) Misdirection: After a Close Combat attack from an enemy succeeds against this character, this character may discard a card. A target enemy in the attacker's engagement range suffers the effects of the attack instead of this character."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1CrimShockAwe00","name":"Shock and Awe","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 9","description":"When this character succeeds on the (1) Trick Action, every friendly character within 6 yards and line of sight of the target also gains the Action's benefits."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G1CrimNimble0000","name":"Nimble","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-purple.webp","system":{"pursuit":"Criminal","requirements":"Step 10","description":"This character generates 1 additional AP on her turn that can only be used for a Movement General Action."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
